1
00:53:27,610 --> 00:53:29,990
[NAPOLEON:] Who is

2
00:53:30,070 --> 00:53:32,700
This ghostly maid

3
00:53:33,450 --> 00:53:35,740
appearing

4
00:53:36,320 --> 00:53:38,950
in my presence?

5
00:53:39,790 --> 00:53:45,040
Who is this spectral form?

6
00:53:45,750 --> 00:53:49,800
[FOLLOWER:] It's Joan of Arc,
Queen of France.

7
00:53:51,260 --> 00:53:52,260
[NAPOLEON:] Ah.

8
00:53:52,300 --> 00:53:54,300
So this is Joan of Arc.

9
00:53:54,970 --> 00:53:57,850
I've read about your spark.

10
00:53:57,930 --> 00:53:59,810
You look so small.

11
00:54:00,680 --> 00:54:02,640
Unfit for a war.

12
00:54:04,100 --> 00:54:06,610
I've heard your tale of woes,

13
00:54:06,650 --> 00:54:08,520
But are you she?

14
00:54:08,610 --> 00:54:10,150
The Armored Savioress?

15
00:54:12,650 --> 00:54:14,650
[JOAN:] Your words, not mine.

16
00:54:16,910 --> 00:54:19,530
[NAPOLEON:] What do

17
00:54:19,620 --> 00:54:22,290
you mean by that?

18
00:54:23,870 --> 00:54:28,670
That is not proper reply

19
00:54:29,170 --> 00:54:31,840
Je suis l'Empereur

20
00:54:31,920 --> 00:54:34,550
du Monde, shepherd

21
00:54:35,760 --> 00:54:39,350
Called Queen of the French

22
00:54:40,850 --> 00:54:44,430
How can someone in your state

23
00:54:44,520 --> 00:54:47,310
Be so cool about her fate?

24
00:54:47,900 --> 00:54:49,980
Perplexing circumstance,

25
00:54:50,520 --> 00:54:52,190
this silent queen of France.

26
00:54:54,490 --> 00:54:57,030
Since you fought for The Cross

27
00:54:57,700 --> 00:55:00,200
I am surely not your boss

28
00:55:00,280 --> 00:55:01,870
You're Church's face!

29
00:55:02,700 --> 00:55:03,790
(SMIRKS)

30
00:55:03,870 --> 00:55:05,620
You're Pope's case!

31
00:55:07,420 --> 00:55:11,040
[FOLLOWERS:] Hey Joan, Hey Joan

32
00:55:11,170 --> 00:55:13,460
Joan of Arc

33
00:55:13,550 --> 00:55:19,260
Hey Joan, brave heart

34
00:55:20,140 --> 00:55:23,390
your spark will start

35
00:55:23,430 --> 00:55:26,430
please make it clear

36
00:55:26,690 --> 00:55:28,690
You led men before,

37
00:55:28,730 --> 00:55:34,650
Why are you here?
